# closeeye-next/ (Next.js) is the single Close Eye product, deployed from this
# repo (the Vercel project's Root Directory = closeeye-next). Vercel reads this
# root .vercelignore during upload, so exclude ONLY the heavy folders the web
# build does not need — the native Capacitor shells and the Next build output.
# NEVER exclude any of closeeye-next/'s source, or the build fails with
# "No Next.js version detected".
closeeye-next/android
closeeye-next/ios
closeeye-next/.next
